### Clinical Interpretation:

1. **Primary Risk Factor**: Chronically low HDL cholesterol represents the most significant and persistent cardiovascular risk factor, indicating impaired reverse cholesterol transport

  "sql": "WITH __health_records AS (\n  SELECT\n    record_category,\n    item_description,\n    value_numeric,\n    DATE_PART(YEAR, record_date) AS record_year\n  FROM health_intelligence.health_records.health_records\n), yearly_averages AS (\n  SELECT\n    record_year,\n    CASE WHEN LOWER(item_description) LIKE '%hdl%' THEN AVG(value_numeric) END AS avg_hdl,\n    CASE WHEN LOWER(item_description) LIKE '%ldl%' THEN AVG(value_numeric) END AS avg_ldl,\n    CASE WHEN LOWER(item_description) LIKE '%triglyceride%' THEN AVG(value_numeric) END AS avg_triglycerides,\n    CASE\n      WHEN LOWER(item_description) LIKE '%total cholesterol%'\n      OR LOWER(item_description) LIKE '%cholesterol total%'\n      THEN AVG(value_numeric)\n    END AS avg_total_cholesterol\n  FROM __health_records\n  WHERE\n    record_category = 'LAB'\n    AND record_year BETWEEN 2010 AND 2025\n    AND LOWER(item_description) IN ('hdl cholesterol', 'ldl cholesterol', 'triglycerides', 'total cholesterol')\n  GROUP BY\n    record_year,\n    item_description\n)\nSELECT\n  record_year,\n  MAX(avg_hdl) AS avg_hdl,\n  MAX(avg_ldl) AS avg_ldl,\n  MAX(avg_triglycerides) AS avg_triglycerides,\n  MAX(avg_total_cholesterol) AS avg_total_cholesterol\nFROM yearly_averages\nGROUP BY\n  record_year\nORDER BY\n  record_year DESC NULLS LAST\n -- Generated by Cortex Analyst\n;",

const recentIndex = rawData.length - 2;
if (recentIndex < 0) return 0;
const recent = rawData[recentIndex][metric];
const current = latestData[metric];
if (!recent || !current) return 0;
return ((current - recent) / recent * 100).toFixed(1);
};

// Compute className strings before JSX
const getMetricCardClass = (metric, value) => {
let baseClass = 'rounded-lg p-4 border ';
if (metric === 'hdl') {
return baseClass + (value >= 40 ? 'bg-green-50 border-green-200' : 'bg-red-50 border-red-200');
} else if (metric === 'ldl') {
return baseClass + (value <= 100 ? 'bg-green-50 border-green-200' : 'bg-yellow-50 border-yellow-200');
} else if (metric === 'triglycerides') {
return baseClass + (value <= 150 ? 'bg-green-50 border-green-200' : 'bg-yellow-50 border-yellow-200');
} else {
return baseClass + (value <= 200 ? 'bg-green-50 border-green-200' : 'bg-yellow-50 border-yellow-200');
}
};

const getTrendIconClass = (trend, metric) => {
if (metric === 'hdl') {
return trend > 0 ? 'text-green-600' : 'text-red-600';
} else {
return trend < 0 ? 'text-green-600' : 'text-red-600';
}
};

const getCheckboxClass = (checked) => {
return 'h-4 w-4 rounded ' + (checked ? 'text-blue-600' : 'text-gray-300');
};
